---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Container Candle Making"
  description="Pour and design candles in beautiful containers. Create candles to take home immediately in Centerville, TN."
  price="$20-28 per person"
  duration="1.5 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="container candles, soy candles, DIY candles, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h1>Container Candle Making - Centerville, TN</h1>
    <p>
      Create beautiful container candles that are ready to use or gift immediately. This quick, fun, and rewarding experience is perfect for busy crafters who want to make something beautiful without a long time commitment.
    </p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>
      You'll pour premium soy wax into gorgeous containers while choosing your fragrance and color. Our instructors ensure your candles turn out beautifully, and unlike some candle-making experiences, your finished candles are ready to use right away—no waiting for curing or cooling at home.
    </p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Selection of beautiful containers</li>
      <li>Premium soy wax</li>
      <li>40+ fragrance options to choose from</li>
      <li>Color customization</li>
      <li>Professional pouring instruction</li>
      <li>Take home immediately—ready to use or gift!</li>
      <li>Create 1-2 beautiful candles per session</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <p>
      Anyone wanting quick results. Great for gift-makers, busy professionals, and anyone who wants to make candles without waiting for the curing process.
    </p>

    <h3>Container Styles Available</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Classic glass jars (8, 16 oz sizes)</li>
      <li>Decorative ceramic containers</li>
      <li>Tin containers for travel</li>
      <li>Premium glass with lids</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and container selection (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Choose fragrance and color (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Hands-on pouring with guidance (30-40 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing touches (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Take home immediately!</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $20-28 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1.5 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> 1-8 people<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Book your container candle experience!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

